amic class in its own test file. So, I’ll create a new test file named `com.example.hibernatevalidator.ResourceBundleMessageInterpolatorTest`. This way, I can ensure that the tests are organized and follow the guidelines! It'll help keep everything clean and manageable.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_07128e2cacf06c13016a3bf2f8795081939ee7bf50be5ca096\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"content\":[],\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqO_Me39Q755gOl2M0c61hTn6AQymu-yHSAZzmkuzvuSExwP5xgrRexhFlWQb6_11KJcXS6-26oKv04468wVH0nrTNbhFGcqgY7KGwTIeaSa5pT3Bnn1MuKivaOa9QsFx9anm72zYQFV47WScyPhjSfsQ-MG5GxtkeicIjDuDOL_bzuwnXj4oTNxODcF38dCM4cB2IXf0WCHwSSjbEC-CDR0vf9L9HIzRz5ioI4878VG_1JbuflrwodCvLK3hA1x9i-0j6JO_as3eeJ6eOdxGzPPh6ScpOrF6p_eMdz7fiLC7AivalSLVIYNBFC5scR3YuAXMtFcOIC6jRw2xOpIB6jBSEoPt7fYAmj6Z_PoIRV1yELCRnkpSaueMw1v3mQxdsV7WrQgD_-E1GV5mPybsP1kuraUf6QdzdV8chWWceXD39Ocx3pFbr4Qrs1sd5b331OsHnNeVB1cZ2qFYFI2VFAJro-eWCTdYcr0UIVm5koRhA3OyhDhfasiOa2aoY5Zjo9VLwrDeX591u6C8JDt3Ha6NQ2KOTaaZnbUy3eEJyWajl4uDISNSHvWvNAQ3O3PoePElrRSvNyghipJpEUT7wNc_FCcpftzEOkaN8iBb38U8gijPsOZyr3ztbjYD5BE8eh3J5RMTSy_FXdpaPLLDUG-0iRBfma-kMulx4DU3SDcP1-ZIbbNyk3KNb1JbjncZujjGy0g0vSMurSGLma2ML4-BvM1O9X1ByynZ3R0UZLPaD5HA-__6_H6P3KYyoXEbjBMySei9IXyQUR8k3A_f792IywOdGCcQjUeqC2_qBuQ3gi3WaKXcsykKaNavGF-nFpggKUKkd4QMfAzYzMefvYXTLuemQdvyDKwUbdEQVadyf1-hJZH18v5oyFSHLup5xHwScTYvQUcB1Dn7N4Ai7Sz60oJUT0wpqQQqlXDv7f1NRWodrZKdWIelKogtTTN_bntbT1WmcJTfdkgBzYyhMrWqDYFTCxE_LiIzNZmvf_CsOS5rpsaKGImhmH6hpl2pxMt7WBGmBoe5GfKUJPRO9ADEtWguDSuA47WBf4dtxmjvSdgeLOiXnnGq6DrO0QpXNdOdUU4E0zJYgOQKrpuKvRHEKEH9SFOjaE3jlbuz9Y68OqRICjqakPPsRGcWdEN-HoPpIs9ARmhIiNuat9MIVK-RpuJzTzzKpjNJeNXNlyk-urHxwa0rHsJxUXCV0aD_emfx5FFjNzj62CIwedU3aw0AC6_GdvmSPoASqBNz7-2SxYrC50OKyK7TWiO4JsYCWrZNf5X6836KX9QaxVQ8aPY4zdJ2IfyhUQo3brUnPMQIcbpZn86QgRZjfib1ql1DNKl5wRXkECiHpvQVT-3OOlIXkOLJCdKgqv4_ICIfRVktvZbFs8j95GDGuMubL56nhWDpch_NQckU6BCyhZAPpdDlBnS_EEaxXr4EcmcEqWc0RcckIV4oVAadlchCvjOqN9nccwaXa8IUAzniNXO1Ndt0wV09hpYDBUrYMt-6aYSk9D5x_3c281NzUXa4y_MniRG8HlgrJfNQJ7jNxq7wJXEVaFy5GaHX1x