6.0.0` so the fallback path can resolve real OSGi API types instead of test stubs.\n\nI did not run or compile the tests, per the workflow instructions.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_07128e2cacf06c13016a3bf35ceb508193a519252e9b1463a0\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1106, "output": 775, "cacheRead": 28672, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 30553, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782313807946, "responseId": "resp_07128e2cacf06c13016a3bf35098608193b8f9e5029e2370de"}, "toolResults": []}
